description: You'll love living in this charming, sunlit penthouse condo in the central part of South Boston, close to the Broadway shops, the SB beaches, and minutes to downtown and the Seaport area. This spacious one-bedroom unit with recent renovations offers an open floor plan, a working kitchen with white solid wood cabinets, granite countertops, a gas stove, stainless steel appliances, and a fabulous skylight flooding the home with light. Off the kitchen is an oversized deck with stunning views; the unit also has exclusive roof rights. Additional amenities include a jacuzzi tub, in-unit laundry, central A/C, and hardwood floors. This a tremendous entry-level unit.
